{
  "texts": [
    "For example, China's policymakers are launching initiatives to allocate computing power to different services and areas to exploit efficiently the country's existing resources and allow different market players to access state-owned or privately owned computers.",
    "67 In a neighbouring field, rules of consumer protection should also be relevant to products like ChatGPT.",
    "68 Finally, rules that seek to protect individuals and groups from discrimination should be fully applicable and applied whenever generative AI is used.",
    "69 Undoubtedly, existing laws that are relevant to generative AI will need to be adapted and tweaked, at least partially, to meet some of the specific challenges raised by this new technology.",
    "In other instances, it will be necessary to clarify the extent to which existing laws do apply to generative AI."
  ]
